# System Components

The interface visualises a complete agent operating system architecture.

Agent Fleet
Distributed AI workers responsible for task execution.

Distributed Execution
Multi-machine orchestration and scalable agent deployment.

Network Topology
Visualisation of node connectivity and system structure.

Performance Telemetry
Monitoring of system resources and operational metrics.

Sovereign Layer
Governance layer controlling execution permissions and system rules.

TimeCore
Timestamped event system used for tracing system activity and debugging.

